name: New!!! Diamond Bohemian Collection
description:
Virgin Bohemian hair is a very rare human hair texture.  The hair origins from the Czech Republic and has some similarity to European hair.  It is Very Soft and has a Natural Healthy Shine.  Virgin Bohemian Hair is Versatile to Style…

Available Styles & Lengths from the Diamond Bohemian Collection:
  Body Wave     Straight     Natural Wave     Curly     Kinky-Curly   
    8"-34"           8"-34"          8"-34"          8"-24"       8"-24"


More about our Diamond Bohemian Collection...
100% Unprocessed Virgin Hair, Grades 5A & 6A Top Quality
4 ounce Bundles
Each Bundle Cut From Single Donor
Full Cuticles; All in the same direction from weft to the ends
Reinforced Double Wefts
Tangle free
Minimum Shedding (ALL human hair shed to some degree)
Hair Can Be Colored, Curled, Flat Ironed, etc.
Hair Can Last 2 years or longer with proper care and maintenance.
2 bundles Recommended for a full install.  An additional Bundle may be necessary depending on the lengths selected to achieve your desired maximize volume.
